text: Winchester '73 is a 1950 American western movie directed by Anthony Mann and starring James Stewart, Shelley Winters, Dan Duryea, Stephen McNally, Rock Hudson, Millard Mitchell, Tony Curtis. It was distributed by Universal Pictures and was remade for television in 1967. ==Other websites== * Category:1950 movies Category:1950s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:Movies directed by Anthony Mann
